lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah, uh-huh, check it out
This one's for all my dreamers out there
You know who you are, let's go

[Verse 1]
They said I couldn't make it, told me I'd fall
But I rose from the ashes, standing tall
From the streets to the stage, I paved my own lane
Through the struggle and the pain, I found my fame

Started from the bottom, now I'm on top
Never gonna stop, gotta reach the top spot
Every setback was just a setup for greatness
I turn my dreams into reality, no more waiting
